               <msContents>
                  <summary>F<locus target="#1r">fols. 1r, </locus>-30v Miracles of Mary, arranged for seasons of the year. F<locus target="#1r">1r, </locus>-12v Introduction to the Miracles of Mary, መቅድመ: ተአምረ: ማርያም: ዘሙዓልቃ:, with additional images included. F<locus target="#12v">12v, </locus>-30v: Eleven Miracles of Mary, incomplete at the end. <locus target="#9v">9v, </locus> and passim mentions the owner, ወለተ እግዚእ. <locus target="#12v">12v</locus> offers prayers in the memory of the souls of ገብረ ክርስቶስ,  ኃይለ ማርያም, ወለተ ብርሃን, አመተ ጽዮን, ወለተ ማርያም. Illuminations are added recently over text.</summary>
