                                                  The Virgin, Apostles and others receive communion
                                                  by Jesus</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ተክህነ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ። በዕለተ፡ ፍልሰታ፡ ለወላዲቱ፡ ወዘከመ፡ አቅረቦሙ፡ ለአርድእቱ፡ ወለኵሉ፡ ጉባኤ። ወእምድኅረዝ፡ ኮነ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ካህነ፡ በሥጋ፡ ወላዲቱ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ ማርያም።</incipit></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.5"><locus from="22v" to="24r" facs="026">Fols 22v–24r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5229MiracleJohn">Miracle of
                                                  Mary: St Mary asks that St John be allowed to
                                                  visit her dwelling place</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ዘከመ፡ ሰአለቶ፡ ለወልዳ፡ ከመ፡ ያምጽኦ፡ ለዮሐንስ፡ ወትርአዮ። ጸሎታ፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወጸለየት፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ እንዘ፡ ትብል፡ ኦእግዚእየ፡ ወአምላኪየ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘኀረያ፡ ለአመቱ፡ ድሉተ፡ ለተስብኦቱ።</incipit></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.6"><locus from="24r" to="25r" facs="027">Fols 24r–25r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3671Miracle">Miracle of Mary:
                                                  Miracle of the transmigration of the Virgin
                                                  announced by Gabriel</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ወትቤ፡ እግዝእትነ፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/> እንዘ፡ ሀለወት፡ በቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ኦእግዚእየ፡ ሊቅ፡ ኄር፡ ፈኑ፡ ወአንሥአኒ፡ እምዝ፡ ዓለም፡ ዘምሉዕ፡ ኃዘናት፡ ወሁከታት።</incipit></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.7"><locus from="25r" to="26r" facs="028">Fols 25r–26r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3672Miracle">Miracle of Mary:
