                                                  Apparition of Jesus Christ to the Apostles,
                                                  telling them where to build a church in honour of
                                                  the Virgin</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ወናሁ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ አስተርአየ፡ ማእከሌነ፡ እንዘ፡ ይነብር፡ ዲበ፡ ኪሩቤል፡ ወእሙ፡ ድንግል፡ ትነብር፡ ምስሌሁ።</incipit></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.9"><locus from="27v" to="29r" facs="031">Fols 27v–29r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3629Miracle">Miracle of Mary:
