                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.10"><locus from="29r" to="30v" facs="032">Fols 29r–30v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3686Miracle">Miracle of Mary:
                                                  Narration of St Basil on the apparition of the
                                                  Virgin</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ወእንዘ፡ አነ፡ እነውም፡ ነጸርኩ፡ ራእየ። ወነዋ፡ እሬኢ፡ ብእሲተ፡ ወይእቲ፡ ትበርህ፡ ኵለንታሃ፡ ከመ፡ ፀሐይ።</incipit></msItem>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.11"><locus from="30v" facs="034">Fols 30v and following</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5202MiracleBasilIcon">Miracle of
